"""
AITA for leaving my wife before Christmas
My wife and I have been together just over five years total (3 dating, 2 married) with our 2nd wedding anniversary coming up in December. She's prepping the house for the holidays and is in an overall happy mood. She also has a trip to her grandparents this weekend, she usually visits them once a year around this time. This year will be a bit different as I plan to pack my things and leave her while she's away this weekend. 

&amp;#x200B;

