&amp;#x200B;

So am I the asshole for leaving my wife before Christmas and our 2nd year anniversary?

&amp;#x200B;

TLDR: A year into our marriage my wife has an affair, give her a 2nd chance but affair continues. Plan to leave her this weekend
"""

